    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the thrilling world of ECHO and LULLABY, where surviving the corporations, gangs and mads gods is a daily struggle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Visit the city, its inhabitants and activities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109700/extras/81d0d959fd7c9e445c34748bab043437.apng?t=1771407827\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109700/extras/81d0d959fd7c9e445c34748bab043437.poster.avif?t=1771407827\" class=\"bb_img\" width=51 height=51 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infiltration and Hacking: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock doors, manipulate cameras, hack vending machines, and cybernetic implants to gain the upper hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109700/extras/96913f8e07723e8cfacaa16d9288caf2.poster.avif?t=1771407827\" width=368 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109700/extras/96913f8e07723e8cfacaa16d9288caf2.webm?t=1771407827\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3109700/extras/96913f8e07723e8cfacaa16d9288caf2.mp4?t=1771407827\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategy and Stealth: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize stealth, silence, and hacking attacks to outsmart your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Travel and Exploration: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive to various destinations such as the town of Cynapse, the EdenSynth farm, and the wastelands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Character Customization: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify your character's appearance with different clothes, hairstyles, and hats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Weapons and Companions: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield over 40 weapons, and benefit from the help of 4 passive pets and 4 pets capable of casting 12 different spells (and more)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>bullet hell lite:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you advance in the game you will unlock multiple ways to rain bullets and spells on waves of enemies!! Survive!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to immerse yourself in an epic adventure and every enemy can be outmaneuvered with your hacking and strategic skills. The fate of ECHO and LULLABY is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Thanks to Gamemaker community for help &lt;3</strong></p>",
